Aggregate Functions (COUNT, SUM, AVG, MIN, MAX)

### Practice Questions:

1. Count the total number of patients in the hospital.
2. Calculate the average satisfaction score of all patients.
3. Find the minimum and maximum age of patients.

Challenge Questions: 
Question: Calculate the total number of patients admitted, total patients refused, and the average patient satisfaction across all services and weeks. Round the average satisfaction to 2 decimal places.

***Queries

#1
select count(*) from patients;

#2
select round(avg(satisfaction),2) from patients;

#3
select min(age), max(age) from patients;

#Challenge: 
select sum(patients_admitted), sum(patients_refused), round(avg(patient_satisfaction),2) from services_weekly;

select week, sum(patients_admitted), sum(patients_refused), round(avg(patient_satisfaction),2) from services_weekly
group by week;




